{"tid":1915196,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說「黑警死全家」，試著說「賤賊冚家剷」","createTime":"2020-03-08T04:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T06:25:35.000Z","uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b41c6189696f0fe76eff3dd6bea02117ca5bc1","tid":1915196,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7a3460a0b42c21d07c9760c2b5805c373dbbb6","tid":1915196,"uid":22360,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:59:21.000Z","msg":"不要說話，試著做事"},{"pid":"8224263211bc7d1d01d0c9c95506c24cf907e302","tid":1915196,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:59:36.000Z","msg":"好多channel已經share咗將軍澳警方戰術分析既連登post，氣象巴打想補充四點：<br />\n<br />\n1️⃣現場溝通既問題<br />\n<br />\n唔同防暴小隊既中層指揮官會直接溝通，所以佢地計時間可以好準確。<br />\n<br />\n我方資訊傳遞就比較慢，報哨 &mdash;&gt; 哨台出 &mdash;&gt; 現場睇到，係需要時間，更何況唔係人人都睇實電話。<br />\n<br />\n即使依靠現場傳遞資訊，哨位傳返俾中間（紅星+黃圈）既人，一樣需要時間。<br />\n<br />\n唔完美既改善方法包括：<br />\n👉🏻中間一定要有人負責睇哨台；<br />\n👉🏻哨兵可以同中間一小批人保持直接聯繫；<br />\n👉🏻哨兵要有少少預測能力，睇既範圍亦要大啲。<br />\n<br />\n2️⃣唔好俾229沖昏頭腦，亦唔好抱住狼來了心態<br />\n<br />\n旺角好難完全包抄，四通八達，亦可以透過演技勉強過關。將軍澳完全冇呢啲條件。<br />\n<br />\n警方亦可能玩心理戰，不斷喺外圍兜圈觀察，等人數開始減少或啲人鬆懈先一網打盡。請相信哨兵判斷，並時刻保持警覺。<br />\n<br />\n3️⃣唐明苑一帶可能係警方嘗試既新突破位。另外，一如既往提防便衣用私家車做綁架式拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n4️⃣諗清楚自己行動既目的，唔好為做而做。<br />\n<br />\n《梓樂悼念會》- 預計3月8號黑警喺將軍澳嘅部署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n#安全威脅觀察 #現場注意事項"},{"pid":"601277df2fbbeb5fb1ac040ceb77d3998d5eaeb9","tid":1915196,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:04:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冚家產</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5de3d616aebb32094ba1baa2d3fb0611d7b8bb51","tid":1915196,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:06:26.000Z","msg":"警賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9b247aab4d1c92f465075efbb0eccedfa94b35","tid":1915196,"uid":1042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:09:37.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家 賤賊冚家剷"},{"pid":"1b8ef8988c246c181df5935078154ad44d784e4a","tid":1915196,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b7a3460a0b42c21d07c9760c2b5805c373dbbb6","tid":1915196,"uid":22360,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:59:21.000Z","msg":"不要說話，試著做事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:22:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最重要就係做咗嘅唔撚駛同你交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"fdb8bd953efe21cff3b6536578a44dc354f610f9","tid":1915196,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a9b247aab4d1c92f465075efbb0eccedfa94b35","tid":1915196,"uid":1042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:09:37.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家 賤賊冚家剷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:22:58.000Z","msg":"兩句意思一樣喎<br />\n賤賊=黑警(蚑那化)<br />\n冚家剷=死全家嘅廣東話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人講廣東話</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43215187638b8c48bffb506333e673341bb3150f","tid":1915196,"uid":303304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T06:09:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cc3074da1cf7498c3654f04277b1ca88b7673b4","tid":1915196,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43215187638b8c48bffb506333e673341bb3150f","tid":1915196,"uid":303304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T06:09:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T06:25:35.000Z","msg":"老鳳認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}